{"type": "article", "id": 54180, "title": "耐克前高管任 Reebok 全球创意总监，以及，来看伦敦男装周上的中国设计师 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-06-12T05:15:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 45400, "name": "Reebok"}, {"id": 6424, "name": "Nine West"}, {"id": 1190, "name": "伦敦男装周"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180612130051bxUreW1X8OfS0Rk7.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hermes-international-to-join-paris-cac-40-stockmarket-index-1202696260/\" rel=\"nofollow\">爱马仕国际将成为巴黎股市 CAC-40 指数成分股</a></strong>&nbsp;| 今年以来，爱马仕股价已上涨约 20%。6 月 18 日，爱马仕国际（Hermès International）将加入巴黎 CAC - 40 股市指数。该指数代表了巴黎泛欧交易所市值前一百的公司中 40 家价值最高公司的市值加权指数。开云集团、LVMH 集团及欧莱雅集团也位列其中。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Nine-West-bought-by-ABG-Group-for-340m,986488.html#.Wx9JnjMzY0o\" rel=\"nofollow\">ABG 集团以 3.4 亿美元收购</a></strong><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Nine-West-bought-by-ABG-Group-for-340m,986488.html#.Wx9JnjMzY0o\" rel=\"nofollow\">女鞋品牌 Nine West</a></strong> | 纽约女鞋品牌&nbsp;Nine West 于今年 4 月宣告破产。本周一，美国排名前十的经销商 ABG 集团宣布收购该品牌，同时接管该品牌的所有授权合作伙伴关系及营销活动。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Scene-is-set-for-spectacular-Pitti-Uomo-94-show,986274.html#.Wx9INzMzY0o\" rel=\"nofollow\">第 94 届&nbsp;Pitti Uomo 男装展将于 6 月 12 日至 6 月 15 日举行</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 本季 Pitti Uomo 将有 1240 个品牌参加，比去年新增 20 个。其中 45.2% 来自意大利以外地区，250 个品牌为首次露面。主办方预计将有 3 万人参加展会，其中包括 19400 名买手。买手中约有 8400 人来自意大利以外地区。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/reebok-taps-former-nike-executive-and-brand-specialist-karen-reuther-as-global-creative-director-1202704291/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reebok 任命前耐克高管&nbsp;Karen Reuther 为全球创意总监</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Reebok 未能向母公司主品牌阿迪达斯那样在女性消费者中建立起持续的品牌吸引力，仅上任 18 个月的创意总监&nbsp;Thomas Steinbruck 因此离职。继任者 Karen Reuther 在耐克有 12 年的从业经验，包括担任全球创意总监，统领鞋履、服装及健身器材等的设计策略。加入 Reebok 前，她在波士顿一家设计咨询公司 Cast Collective 工作，客户包括 Puma、Vans、Timberland、Pantone 等。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>除了对比原作及疑似抄袭款设计的 Instagram 账号 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/diet_prada/\" rel=\"nofollow\">@diet_prada</a>，另有一个专门对比类似艺术创作的账号&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/whos____who/\" rel=\"nofollow\">@whos____who</a>&nbsp;也受到了关注。</p><p>不过它不像前者会详细解释出处，除了对比图片只给出艺术家的名字。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121227044Kaslk7utr5AyW1h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>耐克颇具未来感的新系列“Nike React Element 87”将于 6 月 26 日发售（北美地区为 7 月 13 日）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612123224l6gikA9RUsD1P5Cr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612123235HO16hq0DWfNoa5LV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612123246QiEGobuB5nlRqDV7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612123253hBraePLsHKjfVJxD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612123301WHPASdZ83j4e7oLR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>今年是 Lacoste 成立 85 周年。为纪念创始人&nbsp;René Lacoste 设计的经典&nbsp;L.12.12 Polo 衫，该品牌曾于 2011 年推出与之对应的香水系列&nbsp;Eaux L.12.12。<br></p><p>临近夏日，该系列又加入了男女两款新香型“Eau de Lacoste L.12.12 Eau Fraîch”，香味偏清淡，女款外瓶为粉色，男款为青柠色。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612121803QRBmONzH0iyU93Xo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>伦敦男装周继续更新。</p><p>周翔宇的 Xander Zhou 2019 春夏系列再次以“西部世界”为主题。参考 HBO 剧集《西部世界》，周翔宇在新系列中提出了他对未来的三个设想：男性可以怀孕，大人可以穿尿布，上班族可以有三头六臂（“职场哪吒”）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110225f4DSMErwdHjlPNbW.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110235Pqil4MWzvLwnsEg8.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110242ayxLXTd3FNwtoOec.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121102512a5Nr1X0yh4wf6xS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121103003aRXgU0wYFOdtPpM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110308RQWzPgXZUn8b0wpu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110322DFwCxUm8B4urY2Eq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110330m6FsjPVKiXbx0E5y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121103416EDwu1noBkfYXvjc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110351EcrHwOK3jXLB9fxs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110402gidzbDCL3SjhIRQf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110410hVdD6tc2JYEHqLuF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121104203e02nbG7k5OzigoC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121104284i7Oq0VfZUgFnBkE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110438KYZqho5MlygPwdv7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110450ndElah1tpZbyNosj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121104599MItTFcH2wzLGx6C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110508qXU9algQmbu3D7TL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110519eIg3FH8mGNiTqwPz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110528m3QBoxJje6TqKXzG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110537SmJWf2EXUrR7GPdL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110547j6d7eYt8WcMGSpJ3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110556RtUacq3wkHdNsMKY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612110605XVtJrH7yseEhxCUB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>男装品牌 Danshan 由刘丹霞和黄善鹏于 2015 年在伦敦创立。</p><p>2019 年春夏系列仍然延续品牌初创理念：展示男性的脆弱面，打破“责任感、阳刚气质、男子气概”等对男性的单一要求和定义。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612111706EZBLSsTbn9u0drDp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612111720uoy6RjaHUsw2iAVI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612111732x3zqQOl9rAaDIvRP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>李雨山和周俊于 2016 年成立的男装品牌 Pronounce 第三次在伦敦男装周走秀。</p><p>2019 春夏系列的灵感来源是印度恒河边的加尔各答花市。新系列仍然对中山装和工装进行了现代改造，并且延续了人脸印花和出人意料的配色，造型较上季更为简洁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113218NjPqrTJXmuIs5aHA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113231tZgdxSW1KY6zQNvD.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113239L068H7tAVCJbmNDX.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113246OaCwNoE8Yn2Q37Bt.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113253VU0AEvGtdnDzZekH.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113300mkxhMtKw5ZqCJ3BE.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113307ylS5r2zRguZ8dYEs.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113316mruKbZDqReAi9w5O.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113324FXR28uiJplkeWV6G.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113335WXZ0qARG8NKMY3Ed.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113344SKTcs39ZGLg7fnE1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113425Cir0nxSR3y5YvJ6b.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113435zj3E6M82andfWIiL.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113443d4OEUe1M2ZHlnWYN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612113452Oklr1yQLczNDK6XW.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121135457nybwXfZchSGHFYo.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>男装品牌 Private Policy 由李浩冉和瞿思颖在纽约成立，今年是第一次在《智族 GQ》年轻设计师扶持项目的支持下参加伦敦男装周。</p><p>品牌常见元素包括格纹、亮片和&nbsp;BDSM 元素（捆绑与调教等与虐恋相关的人类性行为模式）。《智族 GQ》时装总监陈复原称其“有一股野劲”、“中西夹杂，但很和谐”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114810APipwfnaq6hLe0U3.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114819j7lhIRO1cPF2T5Uu.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114832dAgQS4GwLcFk5TMx.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114843ek89iGxjdPqFzKh4.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114853KUCXhtWj4BzLSdix.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114903q3kEfTImRa1G0JDg.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114912jDsFEaH0gPoyMh9S.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114922NgbI2yUhkxsz6raH.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114931YyotvLk8zJ6qTBNC.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114941vIhOf0mjaDoNLHXS.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612114959FyIuexYC6i82T1z7.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612115012mRPqsBa1ZwKEQeHA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612115024OXyNdSg1l2oVWIi9.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612115034bodwA07DulPMXi8T.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612115044ZO6zsckQ74CMIAGN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.501390\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>周师墨和温雅于 2016 年成立的男装品牌 Staff Only 也是第一次在《智族 GQ》年轻设计师扶持项目的支持下参加伦敦男装周。</p><p>Staff Only 擅长把功能性服装做得有趣且实穿，2019 年春夏系列也延续了这一点。两位设计师这次还做了一些 3D 打印的蛇作为配饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121200326QHwh8cJuOoDP7Tl.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120048ECVRSzKlGiefraqH.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120105LHIlebazDyVs1Zw3.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120119fTICKandO0pmhQAG.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120300IXgeZFGSfHjtRU5k.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121201376jy9eEAUsOSFk1gr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120150FWIG2SqHJe53k4dM.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120217xuwikr1GzWMhjKas.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120232tMD7SjGgXOl5FJwi.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120248saQ6qUb1gEzm5hCl.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120328ZA8DB0qyWkURt4oc.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121203469gKBuEpNkMJXyUnm.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121204041oSaFpBMbqgXT7Wm.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120206LWTBUIQZE10i75oD.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>香港设计师 Key Chow 及 Jarno Leppanen 的男装品牌 Ka Way Key 一向强调亚洲男性背后的感性文化和美学。2019 年春夏系列仍然延续梦幻的色彩以及对材质的强调。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120806z5OgAKqdrxV6XMlv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120825xC3iyM5U4BuYNzRZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806121208382N7K9i8zwGHaBSPO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180612120924OAWG6pRIFXQSEyKD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为 Xander Zhou 2019 SS</p>"}